{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"b9d8e5df-1d78-4f35-bbd8-530b60ea3a6d","content":"This is a well-known MTP behavioral difference. **Microsoft.Testing.Platform returns exit code 8 when zero tests are discovered**, whereas VSTest returned 0. Since your tests are behind `#if INCLUDE_SLOW_TESTS`, configurations without that symbol produce zero tests → exit code 8.\n\n**Fix:** Add this property to your `.csproj`:\n\n```xml\n<TestingPlatformExitCodeOnNoTests>0</TestingPlatformExitCodeOnNoTests>\n```\n\nThis tells MTP to return exit code 0 when no tests are found, matching the old VSTest behavior.","toolRequests":[{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_01QPH78G7pLTYkx363pacUuK","name":"report_intent","arguments":{"intent":"Fixing MTP exit code"},"type":"function"},{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_01Nj53J4hNTWZepqJm4wcu4S","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/sv-9fa086c7c68043e7bb6a3df0858eed72/TestProject.csproj","old_str":"    <EnableMSTestRunner>true</EnableMSTestRunner>\n    <TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport>true</TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport>","new_str":"    <EnableMSTestRunner>true</EnableMSTestRunner>\n    <TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport>true</TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport>\n    <TestingPlatformExitCodeOnNoTests>0</TestingPlatformExitCodeOnNoTests>"},"type":"function","intentionSummary":"edit the file at /tmp/sv-9fa086c7c68043e7bb6a3df0858eed72/TestProject.csproj."}],"interactionId":"7e2dc3a7-552d-4162-b498-a93884a3482b","outputTokens":415,"requestId":"7691:4CC71:E26E174:F897823:69F2A8C5"},"id":"a68efde1-6d31-4dcf-b271-1c1f2c2819f8","timestamp":"2026-04-30T00:56:43.934Z","parentId":"1ed19f5b-d483-4a4f-9d95-147bf01851c1"}
